**                 ***** RULES FOR FOOTBALL *****                    **
**                                                                   **
***********************************************************************
***********************************************************************

 THERE ARE 4 CLOCKED QUARTERS. THE QUARTER DURATION WILL BE SET BEFORE
 KICKOFF. THERE ARE NO TIME-OUT'S ALLOWED.

 TO END THE GAME ENTER 99

 OFFENSIVE PLAYS ARE:

           10 = RUN

           11 = DRAW

           12 = SWEEP

           13 = SCREEN

           14 = SHORT PASS

           15 = LONG PASS

           16 = PUNT

           17 = FIELD GOAL TRY


 DEFENSIVE PLAYS ARE:

           20 = HOLD. USE AGAINST RUN AND DRAW

           21 = NORMAL. USE AGAINST SWEEP AND SCREEN

           22 = BLITZ (RED DOG). USE AGAINST ALL PASSES.

           23 = INTERCEPT. BETTER ODDS FOR PASS INTERCEPTION.

           24 = BLOCK. USE AGAINST ALL KICKS.
